  "notes": "It cannot damage enemies that are already flagged as slag-element spawns. It is especially strong on Gaige, since Close Enough can ricochet missed shots into nearby foes and spread slag more widely. A hotfix on May 11, 2013 increased both its damage and magazine size alongside other Bandit SMGs. It is commonly dropped by Jimbo and Tector Hodunk if you side with the Zafords in Clan Wars, which locks you out of fighting Mick Zaford for the Maggie. You can still farm both in one playthrough by siding with the Zafords, killing only Jimbo and Tector, checking the drop, and then saving and quitting before the mission becomes ready to turn in.",
